reviewText: I love anything that Mark Lowry does, but this DVD doesn't have enough Mark in it. It has so many female singers that I had never heard of, and not nearly enough of Mark singing.

reviewText: While this is a great DVD of mark singing. Most people might be turned off as mark doesn't tell any of his funny stories. But If you want to hear him singing at his best. This DVD is for you!
